        Script
            TBD
            Tool changing
                Intercept M6
                Run macro, eg:
                    Pause the machine (!).
                    Move the spindle to a user-defined "Tool Change Position" (e.g., front of the machine).
                    Wait for you to physically swap the bit.
                    Run a Probe Cycle to measure the new tool length (critical step).
                    Update the Z-zero height to match the new tool length.
                https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2jFvlvu0co&t=1s
